      "instruction": "<p><strong>Boil</strong> a full kettle</p><p><strong>Cook</strong> the pasta in a pot of boiling salted water for 8-10 min or until the pasta is cooked, stirring occasionally, then drain and set aside for step 7 (reserve 1 cup of pasta water)</p>",
