      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, heat a dry wide based pan (large enough to fit the cooked pasta in) on a medium low heat</p><p><strong>When</strong> hot, add the walnuts and toast for 3-5 min, moving them about the pan occasionally so they colour evenly</p><p><strong>Once</strong> toasted, remove them from the heat and reserve the pan for step 7</p>",
