    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the rocket, basil, chopped Parmesan, garlic and toasted walnuts to the food processor</p><p><strong>Add</strong> a large pinch of salt, a good grind of pepper and 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(8 tbsp)</span> of olive oil (extra virgin preferably)</p><p><strong>Blitz</strong> to a paste (if you like your pesto coarse then pulse instead)</p>",
